description:
The story follows the sometimes happy, sometimes sad, and a tad stressful daily life of "some sort of small, cute creature" known as http://anidb.net/ch121969 [Chiikawa]. Chiikawa enjoys delicious food with bees and rabbits, toils hard every day for the rewards of work, and still maintains a smile.
Source: ANN
